title: Imagine a life without Google
description:
Imagine waking up one day to find Google and all of its services gone. Gmail, search, Google Drive, YouTube, Google Home, Google Maps — all gone. In Australia, a world without Google might not be far off. 
Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
itunes:title: Imagine a life without Google
itunes:author: Recode
itunes:subtitle: Australian lawmakers are pushing for some regulations on Google and in response, the Silicon Valley giant has threatened to turn off its services in the country.
